name: Laura Sizemore
about: I am a senior studying Computer Science in the College of Engineering and am minoring in Public Policy & Law and Society. I enjoy using technology to cause a positive impact in my community and beyond. In addition to software development and technical project management, I have experience in full-stack development and data analysis. When I'm not coding, I enjoy reading sci-fi and fantasy novels, playing both board and video games, and spending time with friends.
